"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-soccer-2024-0502-1446962-olympiacos-hammering-leaves-villa-euro-dream-in-tatters\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Aston Villa's hopes of reaching a first European final since 1982 are in tatters after losing 4-2 in the first leg of their Europa Conference League semi-final against Olympiacos.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.007456870234283e-35, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 133, \"end\": 150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7205219860393806e-33, \"text\": \"Conference League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\"}, {\"begin\": 170, \"end\": 180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.580837843963195e-24, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa, playing their biggest occasion in Europe since winning the European Cup 42 years ago, suffered a Greek tragedy as they crumbled on home soil.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 287, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_tragedy\", \"score\": 0.8163251894932747, \"rank\": 0.12398806273405207, \"text\": \"Greek tragedy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_tragedy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_tragedy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ayoub El Kaabi scored a hat-trick and Santiago Hezze's deflected effort made it a memorable night for Nottingham Forest owner Evangelos Marinakis' side.\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 333, \"end\": 347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ayoub El Kaabi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\"}, {\"begin\": 371, \"end\": 379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"score\": 0.9999884714066573, \"rank\": 1.147526080237818e-05, \"text\": \"Santiago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\"}, {\"begin\": 435, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham_Forest_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.687693026214356e-49, \"text\": \"Nottingham Forest\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham_Forest_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nottingham_Forest_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 459, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evangelos_Marinakis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evangelos Marinakis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evangelos_Marinakis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evangelos_Marinakis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa looked primed to take control of the tie after goals either side of half-time from Ollie Watkins and Moussa Diaby had made it 2-2, but they capitulated to concede twice in 11 minutes.\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 576, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ollie_Watkins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ollie Watkins\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ollie_Watkins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ollie_Watkins\"}, {\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moussa Diaby\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even then, they could have boosted their chances but Douglas Luiz missed a penalty in the final 10 minutes.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Luiz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Douglas Luiz\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Luiz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douglas_Luiz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unai Emery is chasing a fifth European trophy, but that now looks unlikely as his side must overturn a two-goal deficit in next week's second leg in Athens.\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 787, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unai_Emery\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Unai Emery\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unai_Emery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unai_Emery\"}, {\"begin\": 936, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9999782463552581, \"rank\": 2.1754010664744118e-05, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that will be a tall order given they have only won two of six European away ties so far this season and Olympiacos is a notoriously tough place to go.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1053, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.580837843963195e-24, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No one was quite expecting exactly how frantic the game would be and the tone was set inside the opening 10 minutes.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympiacos goalkeeper Kostas Tzolakis made a fine save when he flung himself to his left and got fingertips on Morgan Rogers' shot.\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.580837843963195e-24, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Rogers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Morgan Rogers\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Rogers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Rogers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hosts then had the ball in the back of the net when Leon Bailey nodded home from a corner, but Italian referee Marco Guida ruled it out for a foul by Clement Lenglet in the build-up.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1408, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Bailey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leon Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Bailey\"}, {\"begin\": 1451, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.5940386391113267, \"rank\": 0.5065682216810624, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marco_Guida\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marco Guida\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marco_Guida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marco_Guida\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa needed that to count as the tie looked like being taken away from them in a damaging 13-minute spell where they fell 2-0 down.\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympiacos silenced Villa Park when they went ahead in the 17th minute.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.580837843963195e-24, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chiquinho's clever flick set El Kaabi through on goal and he clinically fired past Robin Olsen in front of the Holte End.\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1747, \"end\": 1756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiquinho_(novel)\", \"score\": 0.8423169718119303, \"rank\": 0.10588235294116485, \"text\": \"Chiquinho\", \"types\": [\"Q571\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiquinho_(novel)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiquinho_(novel)\"}, {\"begin\": 1830, \"end\": 1841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robin_Olsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Robin Olsen\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robin_Olsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robin_Olsen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The linesman's flag went up but VAR ruled Matty Cash was playing the visiting striker onside and the goal stood.\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1902, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0451023332160353e-57, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}, {\"begin\": 1912, \"end\": 1922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Cash\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matty Cash\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Cash\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Cash\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa were all at sea and found themselves 2-0 down in the 28th minute as El Kaabi again struck.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The striker benefited from Lucas Digne's failed attempt to play offside and raced on to former Wolves attacker Daniel Podence's through ball to round Olsen and convert.\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2109, \"end\": 2120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucas_Digne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lucas Digne\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucas_Digne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lucas_Digne\"}, {\"begin\": 2193, \"end\": 2207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Podence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daniel Podence\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Podence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Podence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Emery's side were all over the place and could have been three down before half-time but Kostas Fortounis drilled over from a counter-attack.\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2341, \"end\": 2357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kostas_Fortounis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kostas Fortounis\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kostas_Fortounis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kostas_Fortounis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa were getting frustrated by the officious referee, who angered them further when he rejected appeals for a penalty after Bailey went down.\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2521, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.651053505346069e-21, \"text\": \"Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they harnessed that frustration and got back in it on the stroke of half-time.\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a move straight out of the Villa playbook as Cash advanced down the right and fed Diaby, who teed up Watkins to emphatically fire into the bottom corner.\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The start of the second half was delayed by a medical emergency in the crowd, but that did not stop Villa's momentum and they levelled in the 52nd minute.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lenglet's long ball found Bailey, who slipped in Diaby to fire home from an acute angle.\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 3030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2968, \"end\": 2974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.651053505346069e-21, \"text\": \"Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Bailey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At that point, Villa would have expected to go on and take control of the tie, but they wobbled.\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Four minutes later they were back behind as Luiz was penalised when the ball hit his raised arm at a corner and El Kaabi completed his hat-trick when he converted the penalty.\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3174, \"end\": 3178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Luiz_of_Orl\\u00e9ans-Braganza\", \"score\": 0.9730164809600718, \"rank\": 0.013953488372088497, \"text\": \"Luiz\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Luiz_of_Orl\\u00e9ans-Braganza\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Luiz_of_Orl\\u00e9ans-Braganza\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Things got even worse in the 67th minute when Hezze's shot from distance flicked the back of Ezri Konsa and wrong-footed Olsen, who got a hand to it.\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3400, \"end\": 3410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezri_Konsa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ezri Konsa\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezri_Konsa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezri_Konsa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Villa should have reduced their deficit in the 84th minute but Luiz's penalty hit a post after Jhon Duran was bundled over, meaning they must travel to Greece next week and produce a comeback.\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3521, \"end\": 3525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Luiz_of_Orl\\u00e9ans-Braganza\", \"score\": 0.9730164809600718, \"rank\": 0.013953488372088497, \"text\": \"Luiz\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Luiz_of_Orl\\u00e9ans-Braganza\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Luiz_of_Orl\\u00e9ans-Braganza\"}, {\"begin\": 3610, \"end\": 3616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.552256091426081e-18, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Listen to the RT\\u00c9 Soccer podcast onApple Podcasts,Spotifyorwherever you get your podcasts.\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3668, \"end\": 3671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835080660476747, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Source:PA    \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 3746, \"to\": 3770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 3771, \"to\": 3861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3796, \"end\": 3819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851270567, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 3821, \"end\": 3828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 1.7715216599086323e-11, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.\", \"from\": 3862, \"to\": 3928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3862, \"end\": 3865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Images Courtesy of Getty Images.\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3949, \"end\": 3954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.986281953529871, \"rank\": 0.01073620297271968, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}]}"